{"tid":1368560,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯爾在倫敦遭遇持刀暴徒，哥拉辛拿斯空手將其擊退","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:15:24.000Z","uid":235152,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"529a84db40d88e9c4cbf93cd495ebe48ac7fbf4c","tid":1368560,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"香港時間2019年7月26日，阿森納球員厄齊爾在倫敦在遭遇持刀暴徒追逐，同行的科拉希納茨赤手空拳將暴徒擊退。<br />\n<br />\n厄齊爾當時駕駛著自己的黑色奔馳車在倫敦行駛，身後突然出現兩個騎著摩托車的暴徒，持刀追逐厄齊爾的車。<br />\n<br />\n隨後同行的科拉希納茨從這輛價值10萬英鎊的豪車上跳下，赤手空拳地擊退了這兩名匪徒。<br />\n<br />\n波黑後衛科拉希納茨曾經效力於德甲沙爾克04俱樂部，那裡也是厄齊爾出道的地方。<br />\n<br />\n在上賽季的英超聯賽中，科拉希納茨為阿森納出場24次，貢獻了5次助攻的數據。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/sport/football/9586285/kolasinac-video-ozil-car-jack-arsenal-knife-fight/?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=sunfootballtwitter&amp;utm_source=Twitter#Echobox=1564083097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F9586285%2Fkolasinac-video-ozil-car-jack-arsenal-knife-fight%2F%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_campaign%3Dsunfootballtwitter%26utm_source%3DTwitter%23Echobox%3D1564083097&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07i8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=454e2f18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thesun.co.uk/sport/football/9586285/kolasinac-video-ozil-car-jack-arsenal-knife-fight/?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=sunfootballtwitter&amp;utm_source=Twitter#Echobox=1564083097</a>"},{"pid":"c72f92b655bb9d4378dc16b5389329eac4548ef4","tid":1368560,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9e9124dc75ef210c8b7a0022cc28fd46b982da","tid":1368560,"uid":159913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"搞著勇武波斯尼亞黑山佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fe032540da5590bdeabea410ffa3e9b1c9eace","tid":1368560,"uid":218659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"奧斯爾=达哥 哥拉辛拿斯=兄弟"},{"pid":"ec9f21ab10e003dec92c60b2dafe153cc3952966","tid":1368560,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"高人成個頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27865a3513bd9a8423cf34b78aa7140c4b3999c","tid":1368560,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"喺球場上又唔見你咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c039a07fb2fdcab3ef6257e56845a03b417a3b3","tid":1368560,"uid":31905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"唔係好威威串我熱架咩"}]}